    "body": "Prohibit spack from reaching out to ANYTHING over the internet.\r\n\r\n### Rationale\r\n\r\nAt SNL we have a software approval process for certain machines, and I want to ensure that nothing I have not had approved is going to be installed.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nI think I'd just like an option to spack that says \"--no-web\" and forces the use of a local mirror, and prevents any downloading from the web.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\n\r\n### General information\r\n\r\nSpack version: 0.14.2\r\n\r\nAlso this seems related to https://github.com/spack/spack/issues/3321",
    "performed_via_github_app": null
